dialogueSequence.sentence: And alas, woe doth turn my master from me again.
I don’t think that’s even a sentence Slimespeare.
Lo, whomst hails me from yonder road?
Bark Bark (Are all of you like this?)
His fur may be ruff, but he’s very tough.
What can I say, I’m a poet and I didn’t even know it.
Allow me to escort you henceforth.
I was taught to manipulate song to soar through the air.
Maybe a new apprentice will rouse master from his hold at the bar.
